		{
			"id": "grp-checks",
			"type": "group",
			"x": 0,
			"y": 780,
			"width": 2800,
			"height": 720,
			"label": "2 \u00b7 Roadmap checklists (from Roadmap.md)",
			"color": "5"
		},
		{
			"id": "chk-p0p1",
			"type": "text",
			"text": "**Phase 0\u20131**\n\n\u2611 Concept freeze D1\u2013D12\n\u2611 Research brief + roadmap\n\u2611 Free NIM pins + pin log\n\u2611 Docker smoke\n\u2611 Pre-reg experiment YAML\n\u2611 Phase 1 research package",
			"x": 50,
			"y": 880,
			"width": 620,
			"height": 560,
			"color": "4"
		},
		{
			"id": "chk-p2",
			"type": "text",
			"text": "**Phase 2 \u2014 Paper organism**\n\n\u2611 Episode runner + SQLite\n\u2611 Frozen multi-seed fitness\n\u2611 Weight checkpoints (`seo weights`)\n\u2611 Mutation accept / reject loop\n\u2611 Ablation B0 / Bw / Bc / Bcw + \u03b4 report\n\u2611 Evolve schedule / plateau\n\u2611 Docker-isolated candidate eval\n\u2611 Hardened Docker (caps, non-root, RO job)\n\u2611 Schema AST + adversarial tests\n\u2611 Runs/ lab note\n\n\u2611 **\u03b4 success** Bcw \u2265 B0+\u03b4\n   (+4.44 \u00b7 abl_de9d2391b0)",
			"x": 720,
			"y": 880,
			"width": 660,
			"height": 560,
			"color": "3"
		},
		{
			"id": "chk-p3",
			"type": "text",
			"text": "**Phase 3 \u2014 Free LLM pool + critic**\n\n\u2611 Pins: coder / critic / summarizer\n\u2611 Critic taxonomy + mutation gate\n\u2611 Router + session budgets\n\u2611 Summarizer episode distill\n\u2611 `seo metrics` rollup\n\u2611 `seo critic-ab` offline A/B\n\u2611 Live free-NIM field trial\n\u2611 Mutation memory (SQL lessons)\n\u2611 Schema contracts (ticks / choice weights)\n\n\u2611 Soft critic other@conf<0.6 soft_pass\n\u2611 \u03b4 claim success under free NIM",
			"x": 1430,
			"y": 880,
			"width": 660,
			"height": 560,
			"color": "2"
		},
		{
			"id": "chk-p4",
			"type": "text",
			"text": "**Phase 4 \u2014 Observer UI**\n\n\u2611 Population / organism list\n\u2611 Lineage tree\n\u2611 Mutation inspector\n\u2611 Event timeline\n\u2611 Kill switch / pause / freeze\n\u2611 Run-from-UI job console (4.1\u20134.4)\n\u2611 Live logs \u00b7 launch plan \u00b7 final snapshot\n\u2611 Windows-safe job encoding\n\u2611 Watch live video stream + GIF loop\n\n**Phase 5\u20136**\n\n\u2611 Elite archive + parent picker\n\u2611 Auto selection rank / tournament\n\u2611 Multi-lineage budgets + schedule\n\u2611 Multi-agent same-map Watch (viz)\n\u2611 Runs export \u00b7 mutate parse retry\n\u2611 Best-of phenotype \u00b7 weights diagnose\n\u2611 seo doctor (Phase 6 scaffold)\n\u2611 Safety Bc default (diagnose)\n\u2611 Soak harness + reproduce package\n\u2611 Weights --on-seed experiment",
			"x": 2140,
			"y": 880,
			"width": 600,
			"height": 720,
			"color": "1"
		},
		{
			"id": "grp-next",
			"type": "group",
			"x": 0,
			"y": 1560,
			"width": 2800,
			"height": 300,
			"label": "3 \u00b7 Next action + CLI",
			"color": "2"
		},
		{
			"id": "n-next",
			"type": "text",
			"text": "**Next**\n\n1. seo doctor / soak before long live runs\n2. Bc default (diagnose) + best-of Bcw\n3. Seed weight A/B via --on-seed\n4. Live multi-hour soak + lab notes\n\n**CLI:** doctor \u00b7 soak \u00b7 package \u00b7 weights --on-seed\n**Phase 6:** safety + soak + seed train on master",
			"x": 50,
			"y": 1660,
			"width": 1750,
			"height": 160,
			"color": "2"
		},
		{
			"id": "n-cli",
