			"text": "**CLI**\n\nseo doctor \u00b7 soak \u00b7 package\nseo ui \u00b7 runs export\nseo weights holdout|diagnose|--on-seed\nseo mutate [--force-bcw] \u00b7 evolve\nseo watch --multi \u00b7 elite *\nseo ablate | pins",
